A1.7 PROJECT COST The construction cost of this project is estimated at $900,000,000 (2003 dollars).
Additional features and development of other alternatives to satisfy the purpose and need may be
13
identified during the DEIS phase that may increase the overall cost of improvements and mitigation measures.
